as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuvalde-teacher-active-shooter-training-set-children-like-ducks-texas-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eactive%20shooter%3C%2Fa%3E%20inside%20Jackie's%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Numerous%20plushie%20toys%20atop%20a%20child's%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69271393abd5e944effb8c36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221948%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlushies%20left%20on%20Jackie's%20bed%2C%20including%20some%20Build-A-Bears.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Netflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstinct%20made%20me%20drive%20to%20the%20school.%20The%20moment%20I%20was%20on%20the%20main%20highway%2C%20I%20saw%20police%20cars%20and%20other%20law%20enforcement%20vehicles%20rushing%20in%20the%20same%20direction.%20I%20followed%20behind%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20to%20a%20block%20away%20and%20joined%20other%20parents%20who%20had%20gathered%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20fourth-grade%20hallway.%20Then%20we%20heard%20gunfire.%20It%20was%20chaotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22992c967d-a533-4e4f-bf78-65a292db0633%5C%22%3EThe%20hospital%20nurses%20wanted%20to%20speak%20to%20my%20husband%20and%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJavier%20was%20there%20by%20then%2C%20and%20children%20were%20later%20loaded%20onto%20buses.%20But%20they%20couldn't%20find%20Jackie.%20My%20niece%20heard%20that%20they%20were%20taking%20students%20to%20the%20hospital%20and%20headed%20that%20way%20because%20she%20was%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20saw%20an%20ambulance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Femergency-room-what-to-expect%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epulling%20into%20the%20ER%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20little%20girl%20being%20taken%20out%20on%20a%20stretcher.%20She%20looked%20like%20Jackie.%20When%20Javier%20and%20I%20got%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20they%20wouldn't