ill-ready-search-strategy-google-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3EWhy%20Pinterest%20is%20all%20in%20on%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220be6aaae-2b7e-4b52-85a0-d9ee9ce08070%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20some%20key%20GEO%20tips%20from%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Perplexity%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bafca4e-3aa6-4149-8c7b-b8e073de5201%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDanny%20Sullivan%2C%20director%20at%20Google%20Search%2C%20said%20the%20core%20principles%20of%20SEO%20generally%20apply%20to%20new%20forms%20of%20AI%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlenty%20of%20sites%20succeed%20because%20they%20%3Cem%3Edon't%3C%2Fem%3E%20do%20SEO%2C%20or%20hire%20SEOs%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20think%20about%20it%20because%20they're%20just%20focused%20on%20making%20great%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22danny%20sullivan%20google%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6929bfd4abd5e944effbae41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDanny%20Sullivan%2C%20director%20at%20Google%20Search.%3Cp%3EGoogle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGeneral%20website%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.google.com%2Fsearch%2Fblog%2F2025%2F05%2Fsucceeding-in-ai-search%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estructured%20data%20hygiene%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20important%20for%20ensuring%20Google's%20search%20crawlers%20can%20get%20to%20the%20relevant%20content%2C%20Sullivan%20said%2C%20and%20are%20also%20important%20for%20AI%20answers%20because%20they%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20traditional%20search%20results%20at%20their%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20formats%20are%20also%20getting%20better%20at%20multi-modal%20queries%2C%20such%20as%20when%20a%20user%20asks%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20in%20this%20video%3F%26quot%3B%20That's%20an%20extra%20reason%20for%20brands%20to%20incorporate%20more%20images%20and%20videos%2C%20Sullivan%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you've%20still%20been%20a%20text-only%20kind%20of%20player%2C%20more%20images%20and%20videos%20may%20help%20you.%20But%20they%20would%20have%20helped%20you%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESullivan%20said%20any%20GEO%20tools%20that%20advise%20designing%20content%20solely%20for%20rank%20and%20visibility%20purposes%20lose%20%26quot%3Btrack%20of%20the%20big%20picture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20doing%20things%20that%20are%20useful%20for%20human%20beings%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20we%20want%20to%20reward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bcac4802-900a-4c68-8da5-27e344fb1940%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMicrosoft%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKrishna%20Madhavan%2C%20principal%20product%20manager%20for%20Microsoft%20Bing%2C%20said%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20SEO%20are%20still%20critical%2C%20including%20structure%20and%20freshness%20signals%20that%20make%20content%20easier%20for%20AI%20to%20consume.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20using%20Q%26amp%3BA%20sections%2C%20sitemaps%2C%20and%20schema%20%E2%80%94%20a%20code%20that%20helps%20search%20engines%20understand%20sites%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20adopting%20IndexNow%2C%20a%20protocol%20that%20tells%20search%20engines%20when%20a%20site%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStylistically%2C%20Madhavan%20also%20suggests%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.ads.microsoft.com%2Fen%2Fblog%2Fpost%2Foctober-2025%2Foptimizing-your-content-for-inclusion-in-ai-search-answers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elists%20and%20tables%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20long%20walls%20of%20text%2C%20and%20advises%20keeping%20punctuation%20simple%2C%20including%20avoiding%20em%20dashes%20and%20symbols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20to%20win%20remains%20the%20same%3A%20disciplined%20fundamentals%2C%20not%20shortcuts%20or%20hype%2C%20then%20quick%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Madhavan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20new%2C%20Madhavan%20said%2C%20is%20that%20companies%20must%20think%20about%20optimizing%20for%20inclusion%20in%20a%20synthesized%20answer%2C%20rather%20than%20simply%20a%20list%20of%20links%20on%20a%20search%20results%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20beyond%20keywords%20to%20user%20intent%2C%20question%E2%80%91answer%20structure%2C%20and%20machine%E2%80%91readable%20cues%20that%20make%20your%20content%20easy%20to%20parse%2C%26quot%3B%20Madhavan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bdfb2a0-815a-49c3-9519-bd7d070abc32%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerplexity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20benefit%20from%20implying%20that%20they're%20very%20good%20at%20GEO%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jesse%20Dwyer%2C%20head%20of%20communications%20at%20Perplexity.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20tech%20companies%2C%20specifically%20AI%20companies%2C%20who%20benefit%20from%20saying%20that%20it's%20all%20hogwash.%20The%20reality%20is%20always%20somewhere%20in%20between.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20shift%20from%20SEO%20to%20GEO%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20biggest%20mistake%20you%20can%20make%20is%20to%20just%20try%20and%20transfer%20your%20understanding%20apples%20to%20apples%2C%26quot%3B%20Dwyer%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20companies%20offering%20GEO%20services%20are%20doing%20just%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDwyer%20said%20he's%20also%20been%20advising%20marketers%20that%20AI%20search%20will%20shift%20budgets%20toward%20old-fashioned%20brand%20marketing.%20AI%20removes%20the%20%26quot%3Bfriction%26quot%3B%20of%20search%20and%20lets%20people%20buy%20things%20just%20by%20asking%20for%20them.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20building%20a%20strong%20brand%20will%20become%20increasingly%20important%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-geo-tips-ai-search-google-microsoft-perplexity-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764593515000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6929c09589026fbb4d0e999c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-geo-tips-ai-search-google-microsoft-perplexity-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Generative%20engine%20optimization%2C%20GEO%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20marketing%20buzzword.%20Platform%20experts%20give%20their%20advice%20for%20what%20actually%20moves%20the%20needle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly%2CGeoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-geo-tips-ai-search-google-microsoft-perplexity-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kash%20Patel's%20girlfriend%20Alexis%20Wilkins%20speaks%20up%20on%20H-1B%20row%3A%20'We%20do%20not%20want%20this'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764593487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-125695456%2Cimgsize-42428.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fkash-patels-girlfriend-alexis-wilkins-speaks-up-on-h-1b-row-we-do-not-want-this%2Farticleshow%2F125695226.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F125695226.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlexis%20Wilkins%2C%20the%20partner%20of%20FBI%20Director%20Kash%20Patel%2C%20expressed%20her%20concerns%20regarding%20Congressman%20Subramanian%20Raja%20Krishnamoorthy's%20bill%20to%20double%20the%20H-1B%20visa%20cap.%20This%20development%20unfolds%20in%