%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20his%202020%20campaign%20for%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20he%20predicted%20that%20self-driving%20cars%20alone%20could%20displace%20a%20million%20mostly%20male%20truck%20drivers%20with%20limited%20education%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20that%20could%20%26quot%3Bdestabilize%20society%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20trigger%20%26quot%3Briots%20in%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeven%20years%20later%2C%20Yang%20says%20the%20crisis%20he%20feared%20is%20no%20longer%20hypothetical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20aging%20very%2C%20very%20well%2C%20unfortunately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20CNN's%20Michael%20Smerconish%20of%20his%20predictions%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c156a242-bf9c-464d-afef-7d438d9f76a5%5C%22%3EAI%20job%20losses%20are%20no%20longer%20theoretical%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20analyses%20indicate%20that%20AI%20and%20automation%20are%20already%20capable%20of%20performing%20a%20significant%20share%20of%20US%20labor%20tasks%20and%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereshaping%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMIT's%20Iceberg%20Index%2C%20released%20last%20week%2C%20found%20that%20current%20AI%20systems%20can%20already%20technically%20perform%20skills%20representing%2011.7%25%20of%20the%20US%20labor%20market%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20%241.2%20trillion%20in%20wages%20across%20finance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20professional%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20citing%20internal%20Amazon%20strategy%20documents%20and%20interviews%2C%20reported%20in%20October%20that%20the%20company%20believes%20automation%20could%20allow%20it%20to%20avoid%20hiring%20more%20than%20600%2C000%20US%20workers%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20and%20that%20its%20robotics%20team%20has%20an%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20automating%2075%25%20of%20its%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalesforce%2C%20Walmart%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHP%2C%20IBM%2C%20and%20Fiverr%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20all%20cited%20AI%20in%20recent%20rounds%20of%20layoffs%20or%20announced%20layoffs%20tied%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B44%25%20of%20American%20jobs%20are%20either%20repetitive%20manual%20or%20repetitive%20cognitive%20and%20thus%20could%20be%20subject%20to%20AI%20and%20automation%2C%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said%20in%20the%20interview%20with%20CNN.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20seeing%20that%20unfold%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYang's%2044%25%20estimate%20is%20broadly%20in%20line%20with%20some%20major%20studies%20on%20automation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-affect-about-40-percent-global-jobs-imf-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIMF%20analysis%20from%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20around%2060%25%20of%20jobs%20in%20advanced%20economies%20will%20be%20affected%20by%20AI%2C%20with%20half%20benefiting%20from%20the%20technology%20and%20the%20other%20being%20negatively%20impacted%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McKinsey%20Global%20Institute%20(MGI)%20report%20released%20last%20month%20found%20that%20technologies%20could%20theoretically%20automate%20more%20than%20half%20of%20US%20work%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ea38def-7ee5-4eac-9c8a-c17eb6a03220%5C%22%3EYang's%20warning%3A%20Up%20to%2040%20million%20jobs%20could%20vanish%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYang%20pushed%20back%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-safety-pioneer-predicts-ai-could-cause-99-unemployment-by-2030-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoman%20Yampolskiy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Louisville%20and%20an%20AI%20safety%20researcher%2C%20who%20in%20September%20predicted%2099%25%20unemployment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20get%20bad.%20I%20certainly%20don't%20think%2099%25%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Yang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%2044%25%20vulnerability%20benchmark%2C%20Yang%20offered%20a%20rough%20projection%3A%20if%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bchurns%20through%26quot%3B%20even%20half%20of%20those%20jobs%20over%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20the%20country%20could%20see%2030%20to%2040%20million%20positions%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20devastating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20would%20be%20catastrophic%20for%20many%2C%20many%20communities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b31c023b-266f-4607-9d1c-e8b31f0fe7a5%5C%22%3EHis%20fix%3A%20guaranteed%20income%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20companies%20winning%20the%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20pace%20of%20AI-driven%20disruption%20has%20revived%20Yang's%20signature%20policy%20idea%3A%20a%20universal%20basic%20income%20that%20gives%20every%20American%20adult%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20no%20strings%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20guaranteed%20cash%20would%20help%20workers%20survive%20the%20shockwaves%20of%20automation%20and%20maintain%20basic%20economic%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20fund%20a%20nationwide%20program%2C%20Yang%20said%20the%20firms%20driving%20AI's%20explosive%20growth%20should%20bear%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20cited%20Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%2C%20who%20floated%20to%20Axios%20in%20May%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Btoken%20tax%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20government%20should%20levy%20on%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20tech%20giants%20generating%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20billions%26quot%3B%20in%20value%20%E2%80%94%20powered%20in%20part%20by%20data%20the%20public%20never%20knowingly%20provided%20%E2%80%94%20Yang%20said%20an%20AI%20tax%20or%20%26quot%3Bcompute%20tax%26qu