y%20selling%20access%20to%20real%20and%20fake%20AI%20training%20accounts%2C%20which%20contractors%20require%20to%20work%20for%20data-labeling%20companies.%20After%20we%20flagged%20the%20phenomenon%2C%20Meta%20removed%20about%2040%20groups%20and%20pieces%20of%20content%20for%20violating%20its%20policies%20and%20is%20continuing%20to%20investigate%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prominent%20AI%20training%20companies%20ban%20account%20reselling%20and%20say%20they%20have%20safeguards%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20the%20practice.%20But%20what%20are%20purported%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bverified%26quot%3B%20accounts%20continue%20to%20be%20up%20for%20sale%20on%20Facebook%2C%20WhatsApp%2C%20and%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20documents%20show%20Scale%20AI%2C%20which%20received%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-scale-ai-15-billion-alexandr-wang-acquihire-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2414%20billion%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Meta%20in%20June%2C%20has%20been%20battling%20fraudulent%20and%20duplicate%20accounts%20and%20VPN%20misuse%20for%20years%2C%20and%20the%20company%20has%20barred%20users%20from%20some%20countries%20from%20projects%20to%20curb%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20AI%20training%20companies%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-companies-startups-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20billions%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20tech%20giants%20race%20to%20secure%20the%20data%20needed%20to%20train%20their%20AI%20models%20and%20hire%20contractors%2C%20who%20are%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bghost%20workers%26quot%3B%20for%20their%20behind-the-scenes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erole%20in%20AI%20development%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20findings%20show%20how%20AI%20training%2C%20also%20known%20as%20data%20labeling%2C%20is%20attracting%20scammers%20and%20shortcut%20seekers%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20account%20sharing%20that%20happened%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-spark-delivery-app-multiple-accounts-names-verify-identity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20delivery%20and%20ride-hailing%20apps%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20raises%20concerns%20for%20account%20buyers%20and%20sellers%2C%20who%20could%20be%20scammed%20and%20have%20their%20private%20information%20leaked%2C%20and%20for%20the%20clients%20paying%20the%20contracting%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESara%20Saab%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20at%20Prolific%2C%20a%20UK-based%20data-labeling%20startup%2C%20said%20that%20the%20company's%20research%20has%20shown%20that%20no%20single%20fraud%20ring%20is%20behind%20the%20movement%2C%20and%20that%20the%20underground%20industry%20has%20reached%20a%20level%20of%20sophistication%20seen%20in%20bank%20fraud%20or%20concert%20ticket%20scalping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTechnologies%20that%20are%20helping%20data%20labeling%20companies%20are%20also%20helping%20people%20with%20bad%20intentions%2C%20fraudsters%20and%20scammers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22082cc472-9b7c-4548-a7a6-3a3d18e702d7%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20work%20dries%20up%2C%20opportunists%20step%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20contractors%20can%20receive%20tasks%20such%20as%20labeling%20images%20or%20suggesting%20alternative%20chatbot%20responses%2C%20they%20have%20to%20create%20accounts%20and%20complete%20screening%20tests%20on%20platforms%20like%20Scale%20AI-operated%20Outlier%20or%20Surge%20AI-operated%20DataAnnotation.tech.%20The%20work%20is%20remote%2C%20asynchronous%2C%20and%20pay%20can%20hit%20over%20%24100%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlatforms%20like%20Outlier%20offer%20task-based%20projects%20that%20can%20last%20anywhere%20from%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20several%20months%2C%20often%20in%20regions%20where%20language%20translation%20or%20data%20annotation%20work%20is%20needed%2C%20or%20where%20pay%20rates%20are%20lower.%20When%20projects%20dry%20up%2C%20so%20does%20contractors'%20pay.%20That's%20where%20opportunists%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20target%20would-be%20trainers%20by%20selling%20%26quot%3Bverified%26quot%3B%20Outlier%20accounts%20that%20belong%20to%20people%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20the%20US%2C%20where%20projects%20are%20still%20active%2C%20according%20to%20two%20former%20Outlier%20contractors%20in%20Kenya.%20Some%20may%20be%20real%20accounts%2C%20and%20some%20may%20be%20fake%20%E2%80%94%20but%20either%20way%2C%20reselling%20accounts%20is%20barred%20by%20the%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Kenyan%20contractors%2C%20whose%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20said%20they%20personally%20know%20people%20who%20had%20purchased%20accounts.%20They%20added%20that%20some%20also%20bought%20accounts%20if%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20pass%20the%20screening%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccount%20buyers%20use%20tools%20like%20a%20VPN%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bshadow%20proxy%26quot%3B%20to%20mask%20their%20true%20location%20by%20routing%20their%20internet%20connection%20through%20another%20person's%20device%20in%20the%20target%20country%2C%20said%20the%20two%20former%20contractors%20in%20Kenya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20social%20media%20profiles%20that%20claim%20they%20can%20teach%20account%20buyers%20how%20to%20get%20around%20data%20contracting%20companies'%20rules.%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%20YouTube%20channels%20and%20Telegram%20groups%20that%20sell%20would-be%20taskers%20guides%20to%20%26quot%3Bbypass%20geo-restrictions%26quot%3B%20or%20answers%20to%20Outlier's%20onboarding%20tests%20or%20specific%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20%26quot%3Brent%26quot%3B%20out%20their%20accounts%20to%20taskers%20charge%20an%20upfront%20fee%2C%20a%20percentage%20of%20future%20earnings%2C%20or%20both%2C%20according%20to%20four%20contractors%20who%20have%20been%20approached%20by%20people%20looking%20to%20buy%20their%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20found%20one%20paid%20ad%20on%20WhatsApp%20that%20was%20seeking%20to%20purchase%20and%20resell%20verified%20accounts%20for%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20AI%20training%20platforms%2C%20Outlier%20and%20Mercor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f060b82-ec0a-4248-b37b-93565ac47f26%5C%22%3EPlayground%20for%20scammers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20are%20wary%20of%20scams%2C%20two%20contractors%20based%20in%20the%20US%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Buyers%20worry%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bseller%26quot%3B%20may%20take%20payment%20and%20disappear.%20Sellers%20worry%20that%20their%20buyer%20won't%20offer%20them%20a%20percentage%20of%20future%20earnings%20once%20they%20hand%20over%20account%20login%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20posts%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Facebook%20users%20said%20they%20had%20been%20scammed.%20Some%20said%20they%20paid%20for%20an%20AI%20training%20account%2C%20only%20for%20the%20scammer%20to%20block%20them%20and%20disappear%20with%20their%20money.%20Others%20said%20they%20were%20given%20an%20email%20address%20and%20password%20that%20wasn't%20actually%20registered%20with%20an%20AI%20training%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20US%20contractors%20said%20that%20they%20often%20received%20direct%20messages%20on%20Reddit%20from%20people%20seeking%20to%20purchase%20their%20accounts%20after%20they%20passed%20the%20screening%20tests.%20Would-be%20buyers%20offered%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bfair%20payment%26quot%3B%20plus%20an%20unspecified%20cut%20of%20future%20earnings%20made%20via%20the%20account%2C%20according%20to%20a%20chat%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20One%20contractor%20said%20they%20ignore%20the%20requests%20because%20their%20accounts%20could%20be%20banned%20if%20they%20were%20caught.%20Another%20concern%3A%20They%20would%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20income%20taxes%20for%20any%20paid%20work%20performed%20under%20their%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20biggest%20data%20companies%2C%20including%20Scale%20AI%2C%20Mercor%2C%20Prolific%2C%20and%20Surge%20AI%2C%20said%20buying%20and%20selling%20accounts%20is%20banned%20and%20that%20they%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20mechanisms%2C%20from%20monitoring%20Facebook%20groups%20to%20account-level%20pattern%20analysis%2C%20to%20detect%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacebook%20posts%20advertising%20the%20sale%20of%20such%20accounts%20also%20violate%20Meta's%20community%20standards%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftransparency.meta.com%2Fpolicies%2Fcommunity-standards%2Ffraud-and-scams%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efraud%20and%20scams%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20confirmed.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20device%2C%20IP%2C%20and%20behavioral%20safeguards%20to%20identify%20and%20remove%20suspicious%20accounts%20before%20they%20can%20access%20any%20customer%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20Scale%20AI%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcad50f4-0cb9-4563-8a97-1486dc1e5d56%5C%22%3EScale%20AI%20confronts%20'cheaters'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInternal%20Scale%20AI%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20show%20that%20the%20company%2C%20founded%20in%202016%2C%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20scammers%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years.%20On%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-used-chatgpt-to-improve-bard-scale-ai-documents-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproject%20for%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20thousands%20of%20taskers%20were%20flagged%20in%20a%20document%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuspected%20spammers%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcheaters.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%202023%20spreadsheet%20titled%20%26quot%3BGood%20and%20Bad%20Folks%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20called%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20non-US%20taskers%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscale-ai-public-google-docs-security-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScale%20accidentally%20left%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20anyone%20with%20the%20link%2C%20the%20company%20collected%20details%20of%20potential%20fraudsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20spreadsheet%20from%20late%202023%20shows%20rampant%20use%20of%20VPNs%20and%20multiple%20accounts%20belonging%20to%20the%20same%20person.%20The%20document%20contains%20a%20list%20of%20490%20contractors%20that%20were%20removed%3A%2048%20for%20using%20a%20VPN%20and%20a%20digital%20payments%20app%20that%20allows%20users%20to%20withdraw%20money%20in%20US%20dollars%3B%2070%20for%20accounts%20registered%20under%20the%20same%20name%3B%20and%2011%20for%20having%20two%20accounts.%20Another%2021%20users%20were%20removed%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Blow%20quality%26quot%3B%20taskers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20also%20show%20that%20a%20project%20with%20an%20unnamed%20client%20was%20plagued%20with%20quality%20issues.%20In%20one%20project%20progress%20tracking%20document%2C%20Scale%20AI%20managers%20discussed%20various%20strategies%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20ahead%20of%20the%20spammers.%26quot%3B%20They%20included%20banning%20certain%20accounts%20from%20Egypt%2C%20Kenya%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20other%20countries%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20project%20for%20using%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20blocking%20the%20copying%20and%20pasting%20of%20content.%20The%20Kenya-based%20contractors%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20said%20that%20all%20AI%20training%20project%20opportunities%20in%20the%20region%20have%20sharply%20declined%20since%20late%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20black%20market%20for%20Outlier%20accounts%20has%20spurred%20another%20cottage%20industry%3A%20hijacking%20real%20ones.%20Contractors%20have%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Foutlier_ai%2Fcomments%2F1o0ah41%2Fgot_promoted_to_quality_manager_qm_at_outlier_ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efake%20job%20promotion%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20for%20their%20login%20credentials.%20Scale%20AI%20banned%20one%20user%20for%20harvesting%20workers'%20contact%20info%20and%20spamming%20them%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20according%20to%20an%20email%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProlific's%20Saab%20described%20the%20targeting%20of%20AI%20training%20platforms%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Baccelerating%20arms%20race%26quot%3B%20between%20them%20and%20fraudsters%20%E2%80%94%20and%20said%20it%20requires%20proactive%20action%20from%20companies%20to%20stay%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20Shubhangi%20Goel%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asgoel%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Esgoel%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asgoel%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3Eor%20Signal%20at%20shuby.85.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%20here's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-account-selling-market-scam-scale-surge-mercor-facebook-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764589928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69245e41e1a9cbb014ded092%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-account-selling-market-scam-scale-surge-mercor-facebook-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20shadow