acher%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh's%20Naharlagun%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764587313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Foot8t25k_police-generic_625x300_07_November_22.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftuition-teacher-charged-for-sexually-assaulting-4-girls-in-arunachal-pradesh-cops-9730510%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20girls%2C%20all%20aged%20around%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20were%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20their%20private%20tuition%20teacher%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh's%20Naharlagun%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftuition-teacher-charged-for-sexually-assaulting-4-girls-in-arunachal-pradesh-cops-9730510%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20paid%20%241%2C963%20for%20a%2043-hour%20Amtrak%20train%20to%20avoid%20Thanksgiving%20travel%20chaos.%20It%20felt%20like%20stepping%20back%20in%20time.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20selfie%20from%20the%20train.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6927ad4aabd5e944effba0b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20worked%20from%20our%20sleeper%20car%20and%20the%20community%20observation%20car%20during%20the%2043-hour%20train%20ride.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20took%20a%2043-hour%20Amtrak%20train%20ride%20to%20avoid%20chaos%20at%20airports%20ahead%20of%20Thanksgiving.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Southwest%20Chief%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Chicago%20had%20scenic%20views%20and%20a%20community%20vibe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20costs%20more%20and%20takes%20longer%20than%20flying%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20do%20more%20long-haul%20Amtrak%20rides.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20plagues%20of%20our%20modern%20age%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-creating-own-versions-of-landlines-with-cellphones-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escreen%20addiction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20anti-social%20behavior%2C%20and%20a%20desire%20for%20immediate%20gratification%2C%20all%20driven%20by%20the%20supercomputers%20constantly%20affixed%20to%20our%20hands%2C%20then%20Amtrak%20may%20be%20the%20antidote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%2043-hour%2C%202%2C265-mile%20cross-country%20journey%20from%20Los%20Angeles%20to%20Chicago%20on%20Amtrak's%20Southwest%20Chief%2C%20I%20stared%20out%20the%20window%20at%20deep%20red%20mesas%20and%20Midwest%20farmland.%20I%20shared%20meals%20with%20strangers.%20I%20played%20chess%20with%20my%20husband%20while%20others%20watched%20before%20playing%20a%20game%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20train%20for%20two%20reasons.%20First%2C%20to%20avoid%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-what-to-do-if-flight-gets-delayed-or-canceled-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eairport%20chaos%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20often%20accompanies%20Thanksgiving%2C%20typically%20the%20busiest%20time%20of%20year%20for%20air%20travel%20(especially%20because%20there%20was%20a%20possibility%20the%20government%20shutdown%20would%20still%20be%20ongoing).%20Second%2C%20for%20the%20adventure%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20paid%20%241%2C963%20for%20a%20two%20people%20in%20a%20large%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-hour-amtrak-train-overnight-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleeper%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20room.%20While%20it%20was%20a%20lot%20more%20expensive%20and%20took%20much%20longer%20than%20flying%2C%20it%20delivered%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20an%20adventure%20across%20the%20American%20West.%20And%2C%20after%20my%20ride%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20to%20me%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-about-train-travel-from-frequent-amtrak-traveler-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmtrak%20has%20reached%3C%2Fa%3E%20record%20ridership%20and%20revenue%2C%20with%2034.5%20million%20customer%20trips%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%20that%20ended%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bed%20folded%20out.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69279e9789026fbb4d0e8b27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Amtrak%20Family%20room%20had%20two%20lower%20beds%20and%20two%20upper%20bunks%20that%20folded%20down.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bench%20in%20sleeper%20car.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69279ed289026fbb4d0e8b2b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20pulled%20out%20one%20bed%20that%20we%20shared%20and%20left%20the%20benches%20up%20on%20the%20other%20side.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhereas%20plane%20rides%20have%20increasingly%20become%20an%20impersonal%2C%20stress-inducing%20experience%20that%20often%20feels%20like%20a%20glorified%20commuter%20bus%2C%20the%20Amtrak%20feels%20a%20bit%20stuck%20in%20time%2C%20but%20in%20a%20good%20way%20%E2%80%94%20slower%2C%20more%20communal%2C%20less%20rigid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22af8cb037-26a9-4c95-a91f-c082ed3cc428%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20had%20a%20large%2C%20cozy%20room%20with%20plenty%20of%20space%20for%202%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20left%20from%20Los%20Angeles's%20Union%20Station%20the%20Monday%20before%20Thanksgiving%20shortly%20after%205%20p.m.%20local%20time.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20Southwest%20Chief%20would%20take%20us%20through%20