thers%20in%20our%20sleeper%20car.%20The%20bathrooms%20were%20clean%20and%20well-maintained%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20larger%20than%20an%20airplane%20bathroom%2C%20while%20the%20shower%20was%20surprisingly%20spacious%20with%20solid%20water%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attendant%20for%20our%20sleeper%20car%20brewed%20a%20fresh%20pot%20of%20coffee%20for%20all%20of%20us%20every%20morning%2C%20and%20had%20a%20sign-up%20sheet%20so%20we%20could%20flag%20when%20we%20were%20ready%20for%20our%20bed%20to%20be%20made%20up%20or%20folded%20away%20each%20morning%20and%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e7ae384-1709-47f2-8309-000ba038968e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20spaces%20are%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20taking%20the%20train%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20eat%2C%20we%20ascended%20to%20the%20dining%20car%2C%20as%20our%20tickets%20came%20with%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dining%20cart%20on%20Amtrak's%20Southwest%20Chief.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F692794e889026fbb4d0e8af5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmtrak's%20traditional%20dining%20cart%20includes%20communal%20seating.%3Cp%3EKelsey%20Vlamis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmtrak%20offers%20a%20traditional%20dining%20service%2C%20also%20known%20as%20shared%20dining.%20That%20means%2C%20unless%20you're%20in%20a%20group%20of%20four%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20sat%20next%20to%20strangers.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-dining-trends-communal-table-restaurants-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommunal%20dining%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20general%20is%20a%20divisive%20trend%2C%20it%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20charm%20of%20taking%20the%20Amtrak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pasta%20dish%20and%20salmon%20dish.%5