-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epricey%20colonoscopy%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20all%20to%20learn%20that%20I%20had%20hemorrhoids%2C%20which%20could%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20lower-fiber%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20later%20learned%2C%20most%20Americans%20don't%20eat%20enough%20fiber%2C%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20a%20healthy%20gut%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20colon%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20aim%20for%20my%20recommended%2025%20grams%20of%20fiber%20a%20day%20(without%20sacrificing%20the%2053%20recommended%20grams%20of%20protein%20a%20day)%2C%20I'd%20have%20to%20get%20creative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7b5a2d3-111e-4816-a33d-8baae632d49e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20stick%20to%20a%20fiber-filled%20breakfast%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20boring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oats%20with%20fruit%20and%20peanut%20butter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69273d9689026fbb4d0e7f1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOatmeal%20with%20berries%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20chia%20seeds%20is%20packed%20with%20fiber%20and%20protein.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%2C%20who's%20always%20been%20a%20fiber%20fan%2C%20makes%20us%20the%20same%20breakfast%20every%20weekday%3A%20oatmeal%20with%20frozen%20berries%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20chia%20seeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20this%2C%20it%20got%20boring%20for%20me.%20I%20started%20enticing%20us%20with%20local%20pastries%20or%20the%20aforementioned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-high-protein-cottage-cheese-recipe-tiktok-pasta-eggs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecottage%20cheese%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Or%2C%20when%20I'd%20go%20to%20the%20office%2C%20I'd%20skip%20the%20at-home%20breakfast%20for%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Edeep%20breath%3C%2Fem%3E%20%