5%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20businessman%20had%20come%20to%20our%20village%20and%20advertised%20about%20aloe%20vera%20farming.%20He%20distributed%20pamphlets%20wherein%20farmers%20had%20stacks%20of%20money%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20the%20other.%20It%20mentioned%20%E2%80%98Aloe%20vera%20%3Cem%3Elagaiye%20aur%20lakho%20kamaiye%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grow%20aloe%20vera%20and%20earn%20in%20lakhs)%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20farmer%20Hrushikesh%20Jayasing%20Dhane%20(44).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenced%20by%20this%2C%20several%20farmers%20bought%20thousands%20of%20plants%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301751%2Fbusiness-school-grad-leaves-london-to-organic-farm-help-farmers-earn-jaivik-jeevan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanted%20them%20on%20their%20barren%20lands%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimagining%20themselves%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20advertisement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20crop%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20doubts%20about%20it.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20market.%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20told%20about%2010%20such%20farmers%20who%20earned%20lakhs%20from%20aloe%20vera.%20The%20local%20officials%20got%20angry%20and%20threw%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20harvesting%20period%20came%20in%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20the%20businessman%20had%20run%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20a%20fraud.%20I%20saw%20farmers%20crying.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20strategy%20to%20market%20the%20crop%2C%20so%20they%20started%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELife%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20a%20humble%20family%20of%20farmers%2C%20Hrushikesh%20owned%20eight%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Padali%20village.%20The%20family%20had%20traditionally%20been%20growing%20crops%20like%20paddy%2C%20pearl%20millet%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20wheat.%20Despite%20toiling%20hard%20on%20the%20field%2C%20they%20would%20not%20get%20sufficient%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20entirely%20dependent%20on%20rainwater%20for%20irrigation%2C%20as%20the%20nearest%20river%20was%20four%20kilometres%20away%2C%20and%20we%20lacked%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20for%20lift%20irrigation.%20Consequently%2C%20our%20crops%20often%20dried%20up.%20Despite%20having%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20land%2C%20it%20remained%20barren%20for%20much%20of%20the%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20four%20was%20dependent%20on%20their%20father%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20salary%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20%3Cem%3Ekachha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud)%20home.%20Such%20was%20the%20financial%20status%20of%20the%20family%20that%20they%20survived%20on%20low-quality%20sorghum%20%3Cem%3Echapatis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%2C%20and%20occasionally%2C%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Class%2010%2C%20Hrushikesh%20never%20wore%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers.%20At%2020%2C%20to%20supplement%20his%20family%20income%20and%20support%20his%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20started%20working%20for%20a%20marketing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20would%20receive%20Rs%203%2C500%20a%20month%20if%20I%20met%20the%20target%20of%20promoting%20Rs%201%20lakh%20in%20sales.%20This%20income%20was%20not%20fixed%2C%20and%20they%20required%20me%20to%20relocate%2025%20km%20away.%20I%20attempted%20to%20do%20this%20work%20for%20three%20to%20four%20months%2C%20but%20it%20became%20unsustainable%20because%20I%20also%20had%20to%20manage%20my%20field%20responsibilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20fertilisers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-3-1723014113-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20says%20farmers%20can%20earn%20good%20profits%20if%20they%20make%20products%20from%20aloe%20vera%20like%20juice%2C%20soaps%2C%20and%20fertilisers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20run%20a%20business%20from%20the%20village%2C%20he%20started%20a%20nursery%20by%20selling%20moringa%20and%20mango%20saplings.%20However%2C%20this%20business%20would%20peak%20only%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20Gradually%2C%20he%20started%20selling%20fertilisers%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20turning%20point%20came%20into%20his%20life%20in%202007%20when%20farmers%20were%20throwing%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurned%20adversity%20into%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHrushikesh%20planted%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20between%20mango%20and%20%3Cem%3Eamla%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20gooseberry)%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20harm%20in%20growing%20aloe%20vera%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20even%20if%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20generate%20immediate%